Package org.yourcompany.yourproject.Backend.businessLayer.components

Class GateComponent

java.lang.Object
org.yourcompany.yourproject.Backend.businessLayer.components.GateComponent
Direct Known Subclasses:
andd, LED, nott, orr, SubcircuitComponent
public abstract class GateComponent extends Object
Abstract base class for all logic gate components in the circuit simulator. Provides common functionality for input/output management, signal propagation, and visual positioning.
